snippet.title: Sniper Elite V2 Remastered – Graphics Comparison Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy at Amazon (UK) – PS4/Xbox One/Nintendo Switch:  https://amzn.to/33dpUGH 
Buy at Amazon (USA) – PS4: https://amzn.to/2W20Lxh 
Buy at Amazon (USA) – Xbox One: https://amzn.to/2TX7INf 
Buy at Amazon (USA) – Nintendo Switch: https://amzn.to/38HavQj 

Sniper Elite V2 Remastered will bring 1945 Berlin to current platforms with stunning new visuals and a host of new features:

• Enhanced Graphics 
• Assassinate the Führer
• All DLC included
• New playable characters
• Frame-by-frame photo mode
• And more!
